        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Water Advanced Technologies for Efficient Resource Use Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill provides statutory authority for the WaterSense program of the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) and sets forth related requirements. Under the program, the EPA awards grants to provide incentives for consumers to purchase water-efficient products.</p>]]>
        </text>
